data.description:
Welcome home to this charming 3-bed, 2.5-bath townhouse perfectly situated for an easy commute to all areas of Jacksonville. This residence offers a harmonious blend of comfort and accessibility. Featuring brand new flooring throughout, with a fresh and modern ambiance. The open-concept living area seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen, creating an inviting space for both relaxation and entertaining.
The primary bedroom is ensuite. The additional bedrooms are spacious and versatile, perfect for accommodating family members, guests, or transforming into a home office. with the convenience of a dedicated laundry area.
Don't miss the opportunity to make this residence your own and experience the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience.
